# djangoplay-site .gitignore
# Static website — no build step, no dependencies.
# Keep this file minimal and intentional.

# ── OS generated ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
.DS_Store?
._*
.Spotlight-V100
.Trashes
Thumbs.db
ehthumbs.db
desktop.ini

# ── Editor / IDE ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# ── Temporary / local files ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.log
*.tmp
*.bak
*.orig

# ── Local development server output ──────────────────────────────────────────
# python3 -m http.server writes nothing, but npx serve creates this:
.cache/
.venv
filemerger-output.txt
project_tree.txt

# ── Private / sensitive ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Never commit real photos or credentials here.
# Profile photos are uploaded directly to the server — not committed.
# See README.md → Profile photo section.
assets/brand/*

# ── Deploy artifacts ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# deploy.sh is committed, but any generated output is not.
.history
assets/json/site_config.json
!dist/
*git-diff-patch-with-stats*